'''昆瑙·纳亚尔'''（Kunal Nayyar，{{bd|1981年|4月30日|}}）是印度[[演员|演员]]。出生于[[英格兰|英格兰]][[伦敦|伦敦]]，在[[印度|印度]]首都[[新德里|新德里]]长大。他饰演的最为人知的角色是美剧《[[生活大爆炸|生活大爆炸]]》里的印度[[天文学家|天文学家]][[拉杰什·库斯拉帕里|拉杰什·库斯拉帕里]]（Rajesh Koothrappali）。昆瑙被《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》雜誌列為2015年及2018年全球收入第三高的電視演員，年收入分別為2千萬及2.35千萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www3.forbes.com/business/the-worlds-highest-paid-tv-actors-2015/12/|title=The World's Highest-Paid TV Actors|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|access-date=3 February 2020|first=Maggie|last=McGarth|archive-date=2018-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319223831/http://www3.forbes.com/business/the-worlds-highest-paid-tv-actors-2015/12/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/natalierobehmed/2018/10/24/highest-paid-tv-actors-2018-jim-parsons-leads-with-26-5-million/|title=Highest-Paid TV Actors 2018|work=Forbes|accessdate=March 21, 2019|first=Natalie|last=Robehmed|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802113835/https://www.forbes.com/sites/natalierobehmed/2018/10/24/highest-paid-tv-actors-2018-jim-parsons-leads-with-26-5-million/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==个人生活==
昆瑙·纳亚尔在伦敦出生，是[[旁遮普人|旁遮普族]]人。4岁时他随家人搬到印度<ref name= accent>{{cite book |title= Yes, My Accent Is Real: And Some Other Things I Haven't Told You |url= https://archive.org/details/yesmyaccentisrea0000nayy |first= Kunal |last= Nayyar |date= 2015 |publisher= Atria Books |isbn= 978-1476761824 }}</ref>。
昆瑙·纳亚尔于2011年底与2006年的[[印度选美小姐|印度选美小姐]]冠军{{le|内娅·卡普尔|Neha Kapur}}结为夫妻<ref name=youtube>{{cite web|title=The Talk, CBS|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uoR5Xdk7kbs|accessdate=3 March 2012|archive-date=2019-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727041331/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uoR5Xdk7kbs&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

